        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Runway offers a more complete all-in-one platform with built-in video editing tools, while Sora has an edge on pure visual fidelity and photorealism. Runway is more controllable with better editing integration, making it better for actual production workflows. Sora is better for generating stunning standalone clips."
      }
    },
